causelist_title.cheader:
FROM 3RD NOVEMBER, 2025 - APPEAL UNDER ARBITRATION ACT, 1940 AND
ARBITRATION AND CONCILIATION ACT, 1996 INCLUDING APPLICATIONS CONNECTED THERETO.

*HABEAS CORPUS PETITION & APPLICATIONS CONNECTED THERETO;

*CONTEMPT APPLICATIONS AND REVIEW PETITIONS (INCLUDING APPLICATIONS
CONNECTED THERETO) OF THE DIVISION BENCH, HON'BLE JUDGES WHEREOF
ARE NOT AVAILABLE DUE TO DEATH, RETIREMENT OR TRANSFER/ELEVATION.

*SHALL TAKE UP ALL MATTERS RELATING TO THE DESIGNATED COURTS FOR MPs/MLAs AS PER THE
JUDGMENT DATED 9TH NOVEMBER, 2023 PASSED BY THE HON'BLE SUPREME COURT OF INDIA
IN WP(C) NO. 699/2016.

*SHALL TAKE UP THE CONTEMPT APPLICATIONS FILED FOLLOWING THE DIRECTION OF THE HON'BLE
SUPREME COURT OF INDIA IN CRIMINAL APPEAL NO. 1277/2014 (ARNESH KUMAR -Vs- STATE OF BIHAR & ANR.).

NOTE 1: APPELLATE SIDE MATTERS WILL BE TAKEN UP ON TUESDAY, WEDNESDAY, THURSDAY AND FRIDAY AFTER RECESS. 

NOTE 2 : ON EVERY TUESDAY AND WEDNESDAY NON COMMERCIAL MATTERS WILL BE TAKEN UP FIRST.
